  <source>Ziv Hospital</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators want to find out if there is any difference between the microbiotic flora
      lining the conjunctiva of medical staff that work in the hospital and others who do not work
      in the hospital.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
